item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】FLAC - TWS - Sparkling Blue (Genie Music FLAC 24bits/96kHz) [2024]
item.description:
Sparkling Blue is the debut mini album by TWS. It was released on January 22, 2024 with "Plot Twist" serving as the album's title track.
"Oh Mymy : 7s" was pre-released on January 2, 2024.
The physical album comes in two versions: Sparkling and Lucky.



Track list
  1. "Plot Twist (첫 만남은 계획대로 되지 않아)" - 2:32
  2. "Unplugged Boy" - 3:08
  3. "First Hooky" - 3:29
  4. "BFF" - 2:47
  5. "Oh Mymy : 7s" - 3:10
